# 2026-07-08 18:08:25.332316
+Improve error handling in sarmkadan/dotnet-micro-orm.
+Work in: /home/redrocket/task-factory/workdir/dotnet-micro-orm
+
+1. Review the main service classes for error handling gaps
+2. Add custom exception types in an Exceptions/ folder:
+   - DotnetMicroOrmException (base)
+   - ConfigurationException
+   - ValidationException (if applicable)
+3. Add proper try-catch blocks where external calls happen (HTTP, DB, file I/O)
+4. Add guard clauses (ArgumentNullException) to public methods missing them
